---
// Webflow's edge 301-strips trailing slashes (/docs/ → /docs).
// Cloudflare Workers Static Assets 307-adds them back for any
// prerendered index.html (/docs → /docs/). The two fight forever.
//
// This SSR page replaces the prerendered index so there is no static
// index.html for the assets layer to match. Astro.rewrite() renders
// the /home route content internally — the browser stays on /docs and
// gets a single 200 response.
return Astro.rewrite('/home');
---
